      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and represents a rare opportunity for a serious collector or enthusiast. The original paint is flawless with no chips or scratches, and the interior remains in showroom condition, still smelling new. Mechanically, it is perfect, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by certified specialists. Every feature works exactly as it did the day it left the factory, making this one of the finest examples available on the market today.",
